{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Find the truth in the collapsed world</h2>The girl awakens from a world of nothing, and in front of her eyes appears a giant mirror that towers above the clouds. She's drawn to the beautiful world reflected in the mirror and reaches out to it. Suddenly, the mirror shattered, and the beautiful world in the mirror falls apart in an instant. When she wakes up again, she is already in the collapsed mirror world, and the hidden truth behind this world will be gradually revealed in the her adventure.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Get immersed in the fascinating world</h2>\u25c6 Beautiful scene<br><br>  \u00b7 Tranquil natural forests, mysterious bell tower, historic ruins of the royal city... The wonderful scenes will bring unique immersive enjoyment.<br>  \u00b7 The beautiful soundtrack created by the Windbell_Project dedicated to bring a more immersive game experience.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1035760/extras/scenary.gif?t=1729530632\" /><br><br>\u25c6 Gripping story<br>  \u00b7 Meet new friends with different personalities, and gradually enrich the inner world of the protagonist Shiro.<br>  \u00b7 Grow up with Shiro and make different choices about the future of the mirror world to reach different endings.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1035760/extras/story.gif?t=1729530632\" /><br><br>\u25c6 Deep and fun combat system <br>  \u00b7 The classic metroidvania level designs, gather the glimmer to converge into a ranged attack to defeat your enemies.<br>  \u00b7 Acquire new skills along the journey, you can explore unknown maps and gradually find out the combat style that suits you.<br>  \u00b7 Collect different mirror spirit companions, each spirit has a unique ability, combine multiple mirror spirit to form a battle strategy unique to you.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.co